Package: LoopRig
Title: A Toolkit for the Integration and Analysis of Chromatin Loop Data
Version: 0.1.1
Date: 2019-12-04
Authors@R: person("Hassaan Maan", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                     email = "hurmaan99@gmail.com") 
Author: Hassaan Maan [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Hassaan Maan <hurmaan99@gmail.com>
Description: This package was developed to address the gap in available R tools for integration of multiple chromatin loop and genomic element datasets. Common coordinate-based workflows involving these datasets are considered and packaged into appropriate customizable functions. 
Depends:
    R (>= 3.4.0)
